name: Iffat Anwar Medical Complex
location: 16 - Awaisia Society, Near Ghazi Chowk College Road, Township, Lahore
about:
At IAMC We are committed to provide quality healthcare in a compassionate, friendly and professional environment in an affordable cost.
For the last 16 years, Iffat Anwar Medical Complex (IAMC) has treated more than 65000 patients suffering from pain, cancer pain and inherited diseases like Muscular Dystrophy, Autism and Cerebral Palsy.

We are a proven leader in Stem Cell Treatment, Regenerative Medicine, Pain Management and Spinal Health Care demonstrating the latest advances in: Non–Operative Procedures, Interventional Pain Management, Acupuncture, Photo Bio Modulation and Physical Therapy.

Our unique practice model provides seamlessly coordinated care under one roof, by the nation’s top specialists resulting in patients returning to their active lifestyles quickly and safely.

This one-stop location offers a state- of- the-art acute care, in rehabilitation –focused on the State of Art congenital pediatric Surgical anomalies, from diagnosis till its complete Rehabilitation, along with reconstructive surgery, Orthopedic surgery, Bone and joint surgery, Eye surgery from cataract to Vitrectomy surgery, ENT surgery, pediatric medicine, oncology, cosmetic Surgery, general surgery, treatment of gynecological Disorders & Obstetrical problems, Internal Medicine, Urological Disorders with complete cure, Faciomaxillaly surgery, Psychiatry etc. all housed in one cooperative health care campus. Placing families in our region who come for care, regardless of whether they are facing physical health challenges. In short Ramzan Ali Syed hospital is a general hospital, serving since ages, which caters for all specialties.

about:

name: Hussain Kidney & Gallstone Hospital
location: 77-Ali Block, New Garden Town, Opp. Barkat Market, behind Total Petrol Pump, Lahore
about:
Hussain Hospital has achieved special expertise in treating kidney tube (ureteral) stones. With advanced, high Tec equipments & vast experience, the stones in whole length of ureter (upper, middle, lower) are broken at the same place without any instrumentation or manipulation or push up endoscopically. We recommend all those patients, suffering from ureteral stones, to contact us & consult your case. By the blessings of Almighty Allah SWT, you will be cured with over the skin ESWL, without any cut, wound, scar, instrumentation or manipulation endo-scopically, bleeding, pain or indoor admission. 
Presently, in the Hospital, thousands of patients from every walk of life, including children, old aged, and students, working women, businessmen, laborers, government servants and VIPs are getting treatment up to their entire satisfactions.
All the staff is cooperative, well trained, dedicated & devoted to its job and carry out its duties with full professional skills. 
Due to God fearing & kind-hearted administration, the poor, needy and deserving patients are also accommodated, paying due considerations to their financial affordability.

The approach of the administration is not commercial rather humanitarian.
The Hospital also has an attached free Clinic, named Altaf Meraj free clinic for helpless and poor patients.
